room_title: Escape room "Wonder Land" by Trapped! Escape Room in Cleveland
room_description:
While wandering you stumble across a strange key hole. Curiosity got the best of you and you wander too far and fall down a long dark hole which leads you to an enchanted strange world. Everything feels like a dream but you canâ€™t wake up. Much to your dismay, you soon realize it is anything but a dream. 
You cross paths with many peculiar characters who in no way help you at all. You are on your own and must pay close attention to what is real and what is not in order to find your way back to reality. 60 minutes is all you have before you are stuck in Wonder Land forever!
